      "duration": "",
      "published_date": "",
      "apple_rating": 0,
      "chunk_text": "總經理交辦一個非常重要的工作給我老闆請他做一份給法人的投資報告結果我老闆出差忘了一干二淨",
      "embedding": [],
      "language": "zh",
      "created_at": "2025-07-10T14:46:13.788302",
      "source_model": "text-embedding-ada-002",
      "tags": "[\"權利保障\", \"投資\", \"職涯\"]"
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "6eced499-a7ea-41f4-99e5-8ed7256398c6",
      "chunk_index": 4,
      "episode_id": "6867815854dac0f7fe975c13",
      "podcast_id": "1304",
